OL,3,CPSNI fined #750,000 for data breach
OL,5,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,6,Fhas been fined #750,000 for an
OL,7,F"egregious" data breach in which the
OL,8,Fpersonal information of staff and
OL,9,Fofficers was released.
OL,11,FThe Information Commissioner's Office
OL,12,F(ICO) fined the organisation for the
OL,13,F"serious" breach that left many PSNI
OL,14,Fworkers fearing for their safety and
OL,15,Fsaid "simple-to-implement" procedures
OL,16,Fcould have prevented it.
