OL,5,FThe ICO had previously announced its
OL,6,Fintention in May to fine the
OL,7,Forganisation #750,000 and Thursday's
OL,8,Fannouncement is confirmation of the
OL,9,Ffinal figure.
OL,11,FThe breach happened in August 2023,
OL,12,Fwhen a spreadsheet released as part of
OL,13,Fa freedom of information request held
OL,14,Fhidden data with the initials,
OL,15,Fsurname, rank and role of all 9,483
OL,16,FPSNI officers and staff.
