OL,5,FPolice later said the information had
OL,6,Fgot into the hands of dissident
OL,7,Frepublicans. In the aftermath of the
OL,8,Fleak, some officers chose to relocate
OL,9,Ftheir homes, cut contact with family
OL,10,Fmembers, and change daily routines.
OL,12,FThe UK data regulator said that the
OL,13,Ffine should have been #5.6 million,
OL,14,Fbut as it was "mindful" of the
OL,15,Ffinancial constraints faced by the
OL,16,FPSNI, it used its discretion to reduce
OL,17,Fthe total amount.
