OL,5,FThe ICO investigation found that the
OL,6,Fbreach caused anxiety and distress for
OL,7,FPSNI staff and officers, with some
OL,8,Fstating that they had left the
OL,9,Forganisation or lost sleep due to
OL,10,Fconcern about their safety.
OL,12,FUK Information Commissioner John
OL,13,FEdwards said it was "a lack of simple,
OL,14,Finternal processes" that led to the
OL,15,F"particularly egregious breach."
OL,17,FHe said it served as "a lesson for all
OL,18,Forganisations" to check their process
OL,19,Faround data protection.
