OL,5,F"In June, that process went before the
OL,6,Fcourts and we accepted liability, so
OL,7,Fthat was committed to in June and the
OL,8,Fcourts are now working through that
OL,9,Fprocess to determine how much exactly
OL,10,Fthat will be," he said.
OL,12,FHe said the #750,000 fine will "add to
OL,13,Fpressures" on "woefully underfunded"
OL,14,Fpolice services.
OL,16,F"We made the representations obviously
OL,17,Fhopeful that there might be an
OL,18,Fadjustment," he said, adding that they
OL,19,Fwould not be appealing the amount.
