OL,5,FPSNI Chief Constable Jon Boutcher said
OL,6,Fthat the service was "in a different
OL,7,Fplace today than we were last August."
OL,9,FHe said that "tireless" work continues
OL,10,Fto "devalue" the compromised dataset,
OL,11,Fand "significant" crime prevention
OL,12,Fadvice has been offered to officers
OL,13,Fand staff.
OL,15,FHe added: "Today's confirmation that
OL,16,Fthe ICO has imposed a #750,000 fine on
OL,17,Fthe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,18,Fis regrettable, especially given the
OL,19,Ffinancial constraints we are currently
OL,20,Ffacing.
